      title: "The story of PAUSE",
      desc: "Together with Danish mental wellness company PauseAble, ustwo has created PAUSE – A totally new relaxation and meditation iPhone experience for a calmer state of mind",
      keywords: "ustwo, mental health, pause, ios, digital design, product design, app design, product development, mindfulness",
      image: "https://usweb-cdn.ustwo.com/ustwo-production/uploads/2015/10/iphone-6-mockup-splash.jpg"
